Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.12,0:00:20.80,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}哼唱的旋律 勾起無盡的思緒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.80,0:00:24.69,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塵封的記憶 閃耀刺眼的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:28.62,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta remember　現在的你仍握有夢的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.62,0:00:32.82,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那時一樣 綻放光芒吧 少年的情懷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:34.82,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在欄杆上刻下將來的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.82,0:00:36.96,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時起我經歷了多少滄桑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.96,0:00:38.87,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在現實與理想的夾縫中搖擺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:41.09,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱情的火焰也已燃燒殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.09,0:00:42.87,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等! 我說等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.87,0:00:45.08,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺起胸膛 勝負才剛剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.08,0:00:47.13,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄的時候就是遊戲結束
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:49.28,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用自己的雙手打破現狀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:50.07,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起來了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.07,0:00:53.30,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們曾為了一線希望而全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.30,0:00:55.24,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了明天而努力生存
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.24,0:00:57.30,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的心情已經忘記了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:00:58.98,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青春沒有極限
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:01:01.99,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇心和年齡無關 我是這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.99,0:01:03.12,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:05.60,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We wanna make the fream come true　所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.60,0:01:09.53,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綻放吧 綻放吧 綻放吧 熱情之花綻放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.53,0:01:12.73,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綻放吧 綻放吧 綻放吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.73,0:01:17.57,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼唱的旋律勾起無盡的思緒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.57,0:01:21.73,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塵封的記憶閃耀刺眼的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.73,0:01:25.57,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta remember　現在的你仍握有夢的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.57,0:01:30.47,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}就像那時一樣 綻放光芒吧少年的情懷
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.37,0:22:25.77,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}想要真心喜歡上一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.77,0:22:29.82,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻在害怕內心受到傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.82,0:22:33.93,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明自己什麼也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.93,0:22:37.17,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻只是說出逞強的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.17,0:22:45.19,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏於內心的軟弱 我視而不見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.19,0:22:50.23,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連那種事情 也能輕易驅散的巨大的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.23,0:22:54.26,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於找到了　You are my sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.26,0:22:58.37,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fly away Fly away　如果和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.37,0:23:02.47,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fly away Fly away　就不會感到害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.47,0:23:06.33,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fly away Fly away　即使失敗也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.33,0:23:10.21,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go another place　Take it easy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.21,0:23:14.47,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fly away Fly away　讓我飛上藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.47,0:23:18.66,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fly away Fly away　不再感到迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:22.55,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fly away Fly away　這都是因為有你在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.55,0:23:28.41,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1500)}Take my chance　Believe in myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.29,0:23:45.02,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Take it easy
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.00,0:01:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,街上好像沒有人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.80,0:01:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺跡發掘現場那邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正要進去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.30,0:01:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優萊卡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.10,0:01:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我們知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.70,0:01:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優萊卡?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 這裡是什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.20,0:02:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光粒子濃度8%
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.40,0:02:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是完全乾涸了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題 這裡也沒人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.10,0:02:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月光號的損傷比預想得要嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.30,0:02:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從上次和科拉利安接觸以後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道為什麼光粒子總是很稀薄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不得不找個地方藏身來進行修理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Opposite View
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.90,0:02:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 你回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.80,0:03:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺不安?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟這裡是軍隊管轄的地區
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會碰到什麼意外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.80,0:03:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是因為這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,損傷狀況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有相當面積的反射膜剝離了 恐怕要花些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去裡面看看 軍隊或許會留下食物什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有用得著的物資也順便帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們帶蘭頓一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近我比你能更自如地駕駛尼爾瓦修 就那麼讓你受打擊麼…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也覺得很不可思議呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是不知怎麼就那樣了 這或許是我的才能…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然不是啦 不過說不定我和尼爾瓦修的相性不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者尼爾瓦修覺得我比你更適合駕駛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然…這是不可能的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭頓 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去探險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能找到備用的反射膜就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先得找到動力設備來發電
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到這裡挖得這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的氣味好難聞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬修 你去下邊看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吉 那邊就拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.60,0:06:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯托納去那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.60,0:06:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎麼的…非常困
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道有沒有剩下什麼吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡真了不得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來還有電
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個源泉真的乾涸了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:09:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是發掘當時這麼毫無防備地進來 我們的腦子全要發瘋的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是早就瘋了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.10,0:09:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今我們理所當然地駕駛著挖掘出的LFO馳騁天空
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它們用作殺戮的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有想過為什麼LFO的形態和人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.60,0:09:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在用它乘風破浪的時候 想的一直都是這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿德洛克或許能為我們解答這個問題 不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優萊卡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽在午睡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.20,0:09:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午睡?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個大叔也是在類似這裡的地方挖掘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭討厭討厭討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我疼 我頭疼 疼啊疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮莫奈 你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭討厭討厭 討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你安靜點啊 安妮莫奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要學會忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是產生耐藥性 更難受的是你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:10:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吃的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吉!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 蘭頓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:12:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道真是不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有剩下的披薩 也給大家帶一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也讓優萊卡嘗嘗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好…在這裡睡著了不知道會有多糟糕……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,備用電池呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有 但不太多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 一點都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.30,0:13:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們先回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 蘭頓不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭頓? 跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了…未經允許就吃了那麼多 該怎麼道歉才好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我還是個孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡吧 只有睡眠能帶給你安寧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛魚?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:15:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優萊卡?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優萊卡 你來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.50,0:16:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我…其實…應該跟你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的話其實不是那個意思 但我想可能讓你不高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也說過我能理解機械的感情對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說那是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.20,0:16:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時我很高興咱們的想法一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其實不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許我只是自以為能理解機械的感情而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你應該是真的和尼爾瓦修心靈相通的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.50,0:17:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得 咱們一起也這麼長時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是對於你 對於你的心情 我卻一點都不瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想更多地瞭解你 因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優萊卡 別這樣根本不理我好麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了 優萊卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭頓 你在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優萊卡在眨眼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼這麼慢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是夢? 難道我這又是在科拉利安裡面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:17:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優萊卡 你在看什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯托納 看到蘭頓了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.20,0:18:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 那小子到底去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是夢 肯定是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但因為是夢就可以坐視不管嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能這麼做嗎 蘭頓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我現在只能為你做到這些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.40,0:20:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後或許還會讓你承受更多的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在你就好好休息吧 安妮莫奈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在這
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說蘭頓啊 你怎麼在這裡睡起覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.80,0:21:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.00,0:21:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才…也就是夢裡倒是鼓起勇氣道了歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在還得再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.80,0:21:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.10,0:21:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這洞穴裡 我突然困了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.60,0:21:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.00,0:21:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的事…我想跟你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.90,0:22:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的道歉我剛才聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.60,0:22:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.70,0:22:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.10,0:22:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.10,0:22:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待續
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.30,0:23:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法飛翔的月光號
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.20,0:23:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了修復它的翅膀 人們決定捕捉飛魚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.70,0:23:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年激昂的心 整個世界安靜地與之產生共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.10,0:24:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 Skyrock Gate
